Python Modules

Split code into .py files. import module, from module import name, as aliases.
Python searches sys.path for modules. __name__ is "__main__" when run as script.

Run use_greeting.py from inside this folder so import greeting resolves:
  cd 25_Modules
  python use_greeting.py

See also: https://www.w3schools.com/python/python_modules.asp
